(define/contract (max-sum nums m k)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (letrec ([n (length nums)]
           [check-unique (lambda (sub)
                           (>= (length (remove-duplicates sub)) m))]
           [subarray-sum (lambda (sub)
                           (apply + sub))]
           [find-max-sum (lambda (i max-sum)
                           (if (<= (+ i k) n)
                               (let ([sub (take (drop nums i) k)])
                                 (if (check-unique sub)
                                     (find-max-sum (+ i 1) (max max-sum (subarray-sum sub)))
                                     (find-max-sum (+ i 1) max-sum)))
                               max-sum))])
    (find-max-sum 0 0)))
